text: Anichini is a quite common Florentine surname from Annichini di Bongarden, Deutch "Freelance Mercenary" in 1300, and may refer to: *Assunta Anichini, Florentine children's clothing tailored brand *Luigi Anichini, Ferrara engraver *Cezary Anichini (1787-1861), Polish-Italian architect Category:Italian-language surnames
title: Anichini
